1) Run checkstyle outside of maven, using the CLI, and find and fix the violations being printed.&lt;br /&gt;
2) Remove all unique ids from your checks in your configuration and re-run maven. This may cause issues if you use those IDs for suppressions.

The best way is to go with #1 .

